        <p><strong>Open year-round</strong></p>
<p>November to mid-May: select services available</p>
<p>Victoria Day weekend (mid-May) to October 31: most facilities are open</p>
<p>May and June: limited services available</p>
<p>July and August: full services available</p>
<p>September and October: limited services available</p>
